section.para:
Testcases need to be marked as being a test and can have some
        more annotations.
            Standard testcase documentation block


/**
 * @test
 * @author Your Name <your@email.here>
 */
public function fooReturnsBarForQuux() {
 ...
}

To mark a method as part of the public API, include an
      @api annotation for it in the docblock.
          Defining the public API

          /**
 * This method is part of the public API.
 *
 * @return void
 * @author Your Name <your@email.here>
 * @api
 */
public function fooBar() {
 ...
}

